# EAS uploads from the monorepo root. Exclude local native build trees and
# dependency installs — EAS regenerates ios/ via prebuild and runs pnpm install
# + pod install on the worker. Without this the archive was ~505 MB (mostly
# artifacts/orderly-mobile/android).

**/node_modules/
**/android/
**/ios/
**/.expo/
**/dist/
**/web-build/
**/.kotlin/

*.apk
*.aab
*.ipa
*.jks
*.keystore
*.p8
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
credentials.json
google-services.json

.git/
**/.DS_Store
**/secrets/
*.tsbuildinfo
.metro-health-check*

# Local scratch / deploy helpers — not needed for the mobile binary
scripts/tmp-*
scripts/deploy-*.sh
scripts/pr-body-*.md
artifacts/orderly-mobile/scripts/tmp-*
